hat she and her team would go to at times - backtracking the gorilla trails to check night- and day-nests (I didn't know gorillas built nests!) for evidence of illness or still-births etc - especially since it often seemed to involve sorting through bags of gorilla dung to find what they were after!\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eIt is also amazing to read of her passion and devotion to these animals (hence the ability to withstand the lonely location and basic facilities of her camp) and very sad to read of people who either deliberately set traps for gorillas or set traps for other animals which the gorillas can also get caught in.","rating":3,"shelving":{"__typename":"Shelving","shelf":{"__typename":"Shelf","name":"read","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/2825213?shelf=read"},"taggings":[{"__typename":"Tagging","tag":{"__typename":"Tag","name":"non-fiction","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/2825213?shelf=non-fiction"}}],"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1437823905"},"likeCount":11,"viewerHasLiked":null,"commentCount":4,"viewerCanComment({\"resourceType\":\"review\"})":null},"Book:kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v1.b5OhbU0QtJSgXvtkp9qs4Q":{"id":"kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v1.b5OhbU0QtJSgXvtkp9qs4Q","__typename":"Book"},"User:1174779":{"id":1174779,"__typename":"User","legacyId":1174779,"imageUrlSquare":"https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1471744167i/1174779._UX200_CR0,0,200,200_.jpg","isAuthor":false,"textReviewsCount":31,"viewableName":"Tess","isBlockedByViewer":false,"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/user/show/1174779-tess","contributor":null,"isFollowing":false,"isFriend":false,"followersCount":7},"Review:kca://review:goodreads/amzn1.gr.review:goodreads.v1.AzXY5eOwsfdHGThl6k07mg":{"id":"kca://review:goodreads/amzn1.gr.review:goodreads.v1.AzXY5eOwsfdHGThl6k07mg","__typename":"Review","book":{"__ref":"Book:kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v1.b5OhbU0QtJSgXvtkp9qs4Q"},"creator":{"__ref":"User:1174779"},"r